Utterance.UttText: In bed 1 is James (Jimmy) Martinez 69 yrs old under Dr White.
He is diagnosed with lung cyst on a background of COPD.
He is ex smoker for 30 yrs and stopped smoking for 20 yrs.
He is still the same and stable.
He walks with forearm support frame with 2 assist.
High falls risk and on normal diet.
